headline: Accenture Acquires Award Solutions to Expand Advanced Wireless Technologies Skills Training Content and Capabilities of Accenture LearnVantage
summary: NEW YORK & PLANO, Texas, November 21, 2024--Accenture has acquired Award Solutions, a provider of training and consulting services in advanced wireless and network technologies.

headline: Cerence (CRNC) Reports Q4 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: Cerence (CRNC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 78.13% and 13.85%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
